commit.message: Implemented route search; implemented smooth animation
Created main page with links to contribute and user pages
Clean up - renamed flask functions; minor corrections
Renamed the contribute.html file; changed title of the contribute page
Implemented recording of routes in the json file; added one route; uncommented fitBounds function to view all the recorded routes
Changed json path file structure; added ability to visualise several paths
Added posting of the path coordinates to the server
Implemented back-end that provides the page and the data for the paths; the map is full screen now
